19 // This code is generated from the Microsoft HTML specification of the
20 // WinWord format. Do NOT edit this code, but fix the spec or the script
21 // generating the sources. If you want to add some additional code, some
22 // includes or any other stuff, please add it to the template file!
23 // For information about the script and the "hidden features" please read
24 // the comments at the begin of the script.
25 
26 // If you find bugs or strange behavior please contact Werner Trobin
27 // <trobin@kde.org>

44 FFN::FFN(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, Version version, bool preservePos)
45 {
46  clearInternal();
47  read(stream, version, preservePos);

50 bool FFN::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, Version version, bool preservePos)
51 {
52 
53  U8 shifterU8;
54 
55  if (preservePos)
56  stream->push();
57 
58  cbFfnM1 = stream->readU8();
59  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
60  prq = shifterU8;
61  shifterU8 >>= 2;
62  fTrueType = shifterU8;
63  shifterU8 >>= 1;
64  unused1_3 = shifterU8;
65  shifterU8 >>= 1;
66  ff = shifterU8;
67  shifterU8 >>= 3;
68  unused1_7 = shifterU8;
69  wWeight = stream->readS16();
70  chs = stream->readU8();
71  ixchSzAlt = stream->readU8();
72 
73  U8 remainingSize = cbFfnM1 - 5;
74 
75  if ( version == Word97 ) {
76  for (int _i = 0; _i < (10); ++_i)
77  panose[_i] = stream->readU8();
78  for (int _i = 0; _i < (24); ++_i)
79  fs[_i] = stream->readU8();
80  remainingSize -= 34;
81 
82  // Remaining size in bytes -> shorts
83  remainingSize /= 2;
84  XCHAR *string = new XCHAR[ remainingSize ];
85  for ( int i = 0; i < remainingSize; ++i )
86  string[ i ] = stream->readU16();
87  if ( ixchSzAlt == 0 )
88  xszFfn = UString( reinterpret_cast<const wvWare::UChar *>( string ), remainingSize - 1 );
89  else {
90  xszFfn = UString( reinterpret_cast<const wvWare::UChar *>( string ), ixchSzAlt - 1 );
91  xszFfnAlt = UString( reinterpret_cast<const wvWare::UChar *>( &string[ ixchSzAlt ] ), remainingSize - 1 - ixchSzAlt );
92  }
93  delete [] string;
94  } else {
95  U8 *string = new U8[ remainingSize ];
96  stream->read( string, remainingSize );
97  // ###### Assume plain latin1 strings, maybe we'll have to use a textconverter here...
98  if ( ixchSzAlt == 0 )
99  xszFfn = UString( reinterpret_cast<char *>( string ) );
100  else {
101  xszFfn = UString( reinterpret_cast<char *>( string ) ); // The strings are 0-terminated, according to the SPEC
102  xszFfnAlt = UString( reinterpret_cast<char *>( &string[ ixchSzAlt ] ) );
103  }
104  delete [] string;
105  }
106 
107  if (preservePos)
108  stream->pop();
109  return true;
110 }

113 {
114  clearInternal();
115 }

117 void FFN::clearInternal()
118 {
119  cbFfnM1 = 0;
120  prq = 0;
121  fTrueType = 0;
122  unused1_3 = 0;
123  ff = 0;
124  unused1_7 = 0;
125  wWeight = 0;
126  chs = 0;
127  ixchSzAlt = 0;
128  for (int _i = 0; _i < (10); ++_i)
129  panose[_i] = 0;
130  for (int _i = 0; _i < (24); ++_i)
131  fs[_i] = 0;
132  xszFfn = UString::null;
133  xszFfnAlt = UString::null;
134 }

136 // There can be only one tab at a given position, no matter what the other options are
137 bool operator==( const TabDescriptor &lhs, const TabDescriptor &rhs )
138 {
139  return lhs.dxaTab == rhs.dxaTab;
140 }
141 bool operator!=( const TabDescriptor &lhs, const TabDescriptor &rhs )
142 {
143  return lhs.dxaTab != rhs.dxaTab;
144 }
145 bool operator<( const TabDescriptor &lhs, const TabDescriptor &rhs )
146 {
147  return lhs.dxaTab < rhs.dxaTab;
148 }
149 bool operator>( const TabDescriptor &lhs, const TabDescriptor &rhs )
150 {
151  return lhs.dxaTab > rhs.dxaTab;
152 }

176 bool DTTM::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
177 {
178 
179  U16 shifterU16;
180 
181  if (preservePos)
182  stream->push();
183 
184  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
185  mint = shifterU16;
186  shifterU16 >>= 6;
187  hr = shifterU16;
188  shifterU16 >>= 5;
189  dom = shifterU16;
190  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
191  mon = shifterU16;
192  shifterU16 >>= 4;
193  yr = shifterU16;
194  shifterU16 >>= 9;
195  wdy = shifterU16;
196 
197  if (preservePos)
198  stream->pop();
199  return true;
200 }

212  shifterU16 >>= 5;
213  dom = shifterU16;

220  wdy = shifterU16;

289 bool DOPTYPOGRAPHY::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
290 {
291 
292  U16 shifterU16;
293 
294  if (preservePos)
295  stream->push();
296 
297  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
298  fKerningPunct = shifterU16;
299  shifterU16 >>= 1;
300  iJustification = shifterU16;
301  shifterU16 >>= 2;
302  iLevelOfKinsoku = shifterU16;
303  shifterU16 >>= 2;
304  f2on1 = shifterU16;
305  shifterU16 >>= 1;
306  unused0_6 = shifterU16;
307  cchFollowingPunct = stream->readS16();
308  cchLeadingPunct = stream->readS16();
309  for (int _i = 0; _i < (101); ++_i)
310  rgxchFPunct[_i] = stream->readU16();
311  for (int _i = 0; _i < (51); ++_i)
312  rgxchLPunct[_i] = stream->readU16();
313 
314  if (preservePos)
315  stream->pop();
316  return true;
317 }
318 
319 void DOPTYPOGRAPHY::clear()
320 {
321  fKerningPunct = 0;
322  iJustification = 0;
323  iLevelOfKinsoku = 0;
324  f2on1 = 0;
325  unused0_6 = 0;
326  cchFollowingPunct = 0;
327  cchLeadingPunct = 0;
328  for (int _i = 0; _i < (101); ++_i)
329  rgxchFPunct[_i] = 0;
330  for (int _i = 0; _i < (51); ++_i)
331  rgxchLPunct[_i] = 0;
332 }
333 
334 bool operator==(const DOPTYPOGRAPHY &lhs, const DOPTYPOGRAPHY &rhs)
335 {
336 
337  for (int _i = 0; _i < (101); ++_i) {
338  if (lhs.rgxchFPunct[_i] != rhs.rgxchFPunct[_i])
339  return false;
340  }
341 
342  for (int _i = 0; _i < (51); ++_i) {
343  if (lhs.rgxchLPunct[_i] != rhs.rgxchLPunct[_i])
344  return false;
345  }
346 
347  return lhs.fKerningPunct == rhs.fKerningPunct &&
348  lhs.iJustification == rhs.iJustification &&
349  lhs.iLevelOfKinsoku == rhs.iLevelOfKinsoku &&
350  lhs.f2on1 == rhs.f2on1 &&
351  lhs.unused0_6 == rhs.unused0_6 &&
352  lhs.cchFollowingPunct == rhs.cchFollowingPunct &&
353  lhs.cchLeadingPunct == rhs.cchLeadingPunct;
354 }
355

357 {
358  return !(lhs == rhs);
359 }

509 bool SHD::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
510 {
511 
512  U16 shifterU16;

515  stream->push();

518  icoFore = shifterU16;

605 bool PHE::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
606 {
607 
608  U16 shifterU16;
609 
610  if (preservePos)
611  stream->push();
612 
613  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
614  fSpare = shifterU16;
615  shifterU16 >>= 1;
616  fUnk = shifterU16;
617  shifterU16 >>= 1;
618  fDiffLines = shifterU16;
619  shifterU16 >>= 1;
620  unused0_3 = shifterU16;
621  shifterU16 >>= 5;
622  clMac = shifterU16;
623  unused2 = stream->readU16();
624  dxaCol = stream->readS32();
625  dym = stream->readS32();
626 
627  if (preservePos)
628  stream->pop();
629  return true;
630 }

633 {

635  U16 shifterU16;
636 
637  shifterU16 = readU16(ptr);
638  ptr += sizeof(U16);
639  fSpare = shifterU16;
640  shifterU16 >>= 1;
641  fUnk = shifterU16;
642  shifterU16 >>= 1;
643  fDiffLines = shifterU16;
644  shifterU16 >>= 1;
645  unused0_3 = shifterU16;

647  clMac = shifterU16;
648  unused2 = readU16(ptr);
649  ptr += sizeof(U16);

738 bool BRC::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
739 {
740 
741  U16 shifterU16;
742 
743  if (preservePos)
744  stream->push();
745 
746  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
747  dptLineWidth = shifterU16;
748  shifterU16 >>= 8;
749  brcType = shifterU16;
750  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
751  ico = shifterU16;
752  shifterU16 >>= 8;
753  dptSpace = shifterU16;
754  shifterU16 >>= 5;
755  fShadow = shifterU16;
756  shifterU16 >>= 1;
757  fFrame = shifterU16;
758  shifterU16 >>= 1;
759  unused2_15 = shifterU16;
760 
761  if (preservePos)
762  stream->pop();
763  return true;
764 }

866 {
867 
868  U16 shifterU16;
869 
870  if (preservePos)
871  stream->push();
872 
873  itl = stream->readS16();
874  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
875  fBorders = shifterU16;
876  shifterU16 >>= 1;
877  fShading = shifterU16;
878  shifterU16 >>= 1;
879  fFont = shifterU16;
880  shifterU16 >>= 1;
881  fColor = shifterU16;
882  shifterU16 >>= 1;
883  fBestFit = shifterU16;
884  shifterU16 >>= 1;
885  fHdrRows = shifterU16;
886  shifterU16 >>= 1;
887  fLastRow = shifterU16;
888  shifterU16 >>= 1;
889  fHdrCols = shifterU16;
890  shifterU16 >>= 1;
891  fLastCol = shifterU16;
892  shifterU16 >>= 1;
893  unused2_9 = shifterU16;
894 
895  if (preservePos)
896  stream->pop();
897  return true;
898 }

1024 bool TC::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
1025 {
1026 
1027  U16 shifterU16;
1028 
1029  if (preservePos)
1030  stream->push();
1031 
1032  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
1033  fFirstMerged = shifterU16;
1034  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1035  fMerged = shifterU16;
1036  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1037  fVertical = shifterU16;
1038  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1039  fBackward = shifterU16;
1040  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1041  fRotateFont = shifterU16;
1042  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1043  fVertMerge = shifterU16;
1044  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1045  fVertRestart = shifterU16;
1046  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1047  vertAlign = shifterU16;
1048  shifterU16 >>= 2;
1049  fUnused = shifterU16;
1050  wUnused = stream->readU16();
1051  brcTop.read(stream, false);
1052  brcLeft.read(stream, false);
1053  brcBottom.read(stream, false);
1054  brcRight.read(stream, false);
1055 
1056  if (preservePos)
1057  stream->pop();
1058  return true;
1059 }

1067  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1068  fFirstMerged = shifterU16;
1069  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1070  fMerged = shifterU16;
1071  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1072  fVertical = shifterU16;
1073  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1074  fBackward = shifterU16;
1075  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1076  fRotateFont = shifterU16;
1077  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1078  fVertMerge = shifterU16;
1079  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1080  fVertRestart = shifterU16;
1081  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1082  vertAlign = shifterU16;
1083  shifterU16 >>= 2;
1084  fUnused = shifterU16;
1085  wUnused = readU16(ptr);
1086  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1087  brcTop.readPtr(ptr);
1088  ptr += BRC::sizeOf;
1089  brcLeft.readPtr(ptr);

1091  brcBottom.readPtr(ptr);

1195 bool TAP::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
1196 {
1197 
1198  U16 shifterU16;
1199 
1200  if (preservePos)
1201  stream->push();
1202 
1203  jc = stream->readS16();
1204  dxaGapHalf = stream->readS32();
1205  dyaRowHeight = stream->readS32();
1206  fCantSplit = stream->readU8();
1207  fTableHeader = stream->readU8();
1208  tlp.read(stream, false);
1209  lwHTMLProps = stream->readS32();
1210  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
1211  fCaFull = shifterU16;
1212  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1213  fFirstRow = shifterU16;
1214  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1215  fLastRow = shifterU16;
1216  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1217  fOutline = shifterU16;
1218  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1219  unused20_12 = shifterU16;
1220  itcMac = stream->readS16();
1221  dxaAdjust = stream->readS32();
1222  dxaScale = stream->readS32();
1223  dxsInch = stream->readS32();
1224  // skipping the std::vector rgdxaCenter
1225  // skipping the std::vector rgdxaCenterPrint
1226  // skipping the std::vector rgtc
1227  // skipping the std::vector rgshd
1228  for (int _i = 0; _i < (6); ++_i)
1229  rgbrcTable[_i].read(stream, false);
1230 
1231  if (preservePos)
1232  stream->pop();
1233  return true;
1234 }

1473  fItalic = shifterU8;
1474  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1475  fSmallCaps = shifterU8;
1476  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1477  fCaps = shifterU8;
1478  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1479  fStrike = shifterU8;
1480  shifterU8 = readU8(ptr);
1481  ptr += sizeof(U8);
1482  kul = shifterU8;
1483  shifterU8 >>= 3;
1484  ico = shifterU8;
1485  ftc = readS16(ptr);
1486  ptr += sizeof(S16);
1487  hps = readU16(ptr);
1488  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1489  iStartAt = readU16(ptr);
1490  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1491  dxaIndent = readU16(ptr);
1492  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1493  dxaSpace = readU16(ptr);
1494  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1495  fNumber1 = readU8(ptr);
1496  ptr += sizeof(U8);
1497  fNumberAcross = readU8(ptr);
1498  ptr += sizeof(U8);
1499  fRestartHdn = readU8(ptr);
1500  ptr += sizeof(U8);
1501  fSpareX = readU8(ptr);
1502  ptr += sizeof(U8);
1503  for (int _i = 0; _i < (32); ++_i) {
1504  rgxch[_i] = readU16(ptr);
1505  ptr += sizeof(U16);
1506  }
1507 }

1686 bool ANLV::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
1687 {
1688 
1689  U8 shifterU8;
1690 
1691  if (preservePos)
1692  stream->push();
1693 
1694  nfc = stream->readU8();
1695  cxchTextBefore = stream->readU8();
1696  cxchTextAfter = stream->readU8();
1697  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
1698  jc = shifterU8;
1699  shifterU8 >>= 2;
1700  fPrev = shifterU8;
1701  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1702  fHang = shifterU8;
1703  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1704  fSetBold = shifterU8;
1705  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1706  fSetItalic = shifterU8;
1707  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1708  fSetSmallCaps = shifterU8;
1709  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1710  fSetCaps = shifterU8;
1711  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
1712  fSetStrike = shifterU8;
1713  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1714  fSetKul = shifterU8;
1715  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1716  fPrevSpace = shifterU8;
1717  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1718  fBold = shifterU8;
1719  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1720  fItalic = shifterU8;
1721  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1722  fSmallCaps = shifterU8;
1723  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1724  fCaps = shifterU8;
1725  shifterU8 >>= 1;
1726  fStrike = shifterU8;
1727  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
1728  kul = shifterU8;
1729  shifterU8 >>= 3;
1730  ico = shifterU8;
1731  ftc = stream->readS16();
1732  hps = stream->readU16();
1733  iStartAt = stream->readU16();
1734  dxaIndent = stream->readU16();
1735  dxaSpace = stream->readU16();
1736 
1737  if (preservePos)
1738  stream->pop();
1739  return true;
1740 }

2126 bool BKD::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
2127 {
2128 
2129  U16 shifterU16;
2130 
2131  if (preservePos)
2132  stream->push();
2133 
2134  ipgd = stream->readS16();
2135  dcpDepend = stream->readS16();
2136  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
2137  icol = shifterU16;
2138  shifterU16 >>= 8;

2140  shifterU16 >>= 1;

2952  lines = shifterU8;
2953  unused1 = readU8(ptr);
2954  ptr += sizeof(U8);
2955 }

5006  iStartAt = stream->readU32();
5007  nfc = stream->readU8();
5008  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
5009  jc = shifterU8;
5010  shifterU8 >>= 2;
5011  fLegal = shifterU8;
5012  shifterU8 >>= 1;
5013  fNoRestart = shifterU8;
5014  shifterU8 >>= 1;
5015  fPrev = shifterU8;
5016  shifterU8 >>= 1;
5017  fPrevSpace = shifterU8;
5018  shifterU8 >>= 1;
5019  fWord6 = shifterU8;
5020  shifterU8 >>= 1;
5021  unused5_7 = shifterU8;
5022  for (int _i = 0; _i < (9); ++_i)
5023  rgbxchNums[_i] = stream->readU8();
5024  ixchFollow = stream->readU8();
5025  dxaSpace = stream->readS32();
5026  dxaIndent = stream->readS32();
5027  cbGrpprlChpx = stream->readU8();
5028  cbGrpprlPapx = stream->readU8();
5029  reserved = stream->readU16();
5030 
5031  if (preservePos)
5032  stream->pop();
5033  return true;
5034 }

5945 bool PCD::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
5946 {
5947 
5948  U16 shifterU16;
5949 
5950  if (preservePos)
5951  stream->push();
5952 
5953  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
5954  fNoParaLast = shifterU16;
5955  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5956  fPaphNil = shifterU16;
5957  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5958  fCopied = shifterU16;
5959  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5960  unused0_3 = shifterU16;
5961  shifterU16 >>= 5;
5962  fn = shifterU16;
5963  fc = stream->readU32();
5964  prm.read(stream, false);
5965 
5966  if (preservePos)
5967  stream->pop();
5968  return true;
5969 }

5971 void PCD::readPtr(const U8 *ptr)
5972 {
5973 
5974  U16 shifterU16;
5975 
5976  shifterU16 = readU16(ptr);
5977  ptr += sizeof(U16);
5978  fNoParaLast = shifterU16;
5979  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5980  fPaphNil = shifterU16;
5981  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5982  fCopied = shifterU16;
5983  shifterU16 >>= 1;
5984  unused0_3 = shifterU16;
5985  shifterU16 >>= 5;
5986  fn = shifterU16;
5987  fc = readU32(ptr);
5988  ptr += sizeof(U32);
5989  prm.readPtr(ptr);
5990  ptr += PRM::sizeOf;
5991 }

6223  shifterU16 >>= 1;
6224  fBitmap = shifterU16;
6225  shifterU16 >>= 1;
6226  fDrawHatch = shifterU16;
6227  shifterU16 >>= 1;
6228  fError = shifterU16;
6229  shifterU16 >>= 1;

6233  brcBottom.read(stream, false);
6234  brcRight.read(stream, false);

6236  dyaOrigin = stream->readS16();

6491 bool SEP::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
6492 {
6493 
6494  U16 shifterU16;
6495 
6496  if (preservePos)
6497  stream->push();
6498 
6499  bkc = stream->readU8();
6500  fTitlePage = stream->readU8();
6501  fAutoPgn = stream->readS8();
6502  nfcPgn = stream->readU8();
6503  fUnlocked = stream->readU8();
6504  cnsPgn = stream->readU8();
6505  fPgnRestart = stream->readU8();
6506  fEndNote = stream->readU8();
6507  lnc = stream->readS8();
6508  grpfIhdt = stream->readS8();
6509  nLnnMod = stream->readU16();
6510  dxaLnn = stream->readS32();
6511  dxaPgn = stream->readS16();
6512  dyaPgn = stream->readS16();
6513  fLBetween = stream->readS8();
6514  vjc = stream->readS8();
6515  dmBinFirst = stream->readU16();
6516  dmBinOther = stream->readU16();
6517  dmPaperReq = stream->readU16();
6518  brcTop.read(stream, false);
6519  brcLeft.read(stream, false);
6520  brcBottom.read(stream, false);
6521  brcRight.read(stream, false);
6522  fPropRMark = stream->readS16();
6523  ibstPropRMark = stream->readS16();
6524  dttmPropRMark.read(stream, false);
6525  dxtCharSpace = stream->readS32();
6526  dyaLinePitch = stream->readS32();
6527  clm = stream->readU16();
6528  unused62 = stream->readU16();
6529  dmOrientPage = stream->readU8();
6530  iHeadingPgn = stream->readU8();
6531  pgnStart = stream->readU16();
6532  lnnMin = stream->readS16();
6533  wTextFlow = stream->readU16();
6534  unused72 = stream->readU16();
6535  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
6536  pgbApplyTo = shifterU16;
6537  shifterU16 >>= 3;
6538  pgbPageDepth = shifterU16;
6539  shifterU16 >>= 2;
6540  pgbOffsetFrom = shifterU16;
6541  shifterU16 >>= 3;
6542  unused74_8 = shifterU16;
6543  xaPage = stream->readU32();
6544  yaPage = stream->readU32();
6545  xaPageNUp = stream->readU32();
6546  yaPageNUp = stream->readU32();
6547  dxaLeft = stream->readU32();
6548  dxaRight = stream->readU32();
6549  dyaTop = stream->readS32();
6550  dyaBottom = stream->readS32();
6551  dzaGutter = stream->readU32();
6552  dyaHdrTop = stream->readU32();
6553  dyaHdrBottom = stream->readU32();
6554  ccolM1 = stream->readS16();
6555  fEvenlySpaced = stream->readS8();
6556  unused123 = stream->readU8();
6557  dxaColumns = stream->readS32();
6558  // skipping the std::vector rgdxaColumnWidthSpacing
6559  dxaColumnWidth = stream->readS32();
6560  dmOrientFirst = stream->readU8();
6561  fLayout = stream->readU8();
6562  unused490 = stream->readU16();
6563  olstAnm.read(stream, false);
6564 
6565  if (preservePos)
6566  stream->pop();
6567  return true;
6568 }
